Taking a break is crucial i think, there is a great saying
“Slowing down is sometimes the best way to speed up.” – Mike Vance” 🧘🏻‍♀️
This is the second time in my life i took a long break from social media and art world, because this always leads to huge changes and renewal. 🌞✨
I have butterflies when I imagine and anticipate my new projects, it feels like 1st of September first day of school in a way. 🔥
My Reset was amazing, first time in my life I realized there is no final destination and there is no rush in art, the process is what matters. I realized that ambition can sometimes blind us, confuse us. It is those moments of silent internal monologue when you confess to yourself your true desire in art your true passion. 

I guess great art can only be sincere, there is no place for lie or show off. I am slowly coming back, without any pressure or high expectations, i am coming back to enjoy the process of creation and sharing it with you. 🙌🏻

“What we are waiting for is not as important as what happens to us while we are waiting. Trust the process.” – Mandy Hale
Ur F

Hello to everyone!🔥🙌🏻 

This is my first giveaway, maybe the last one, i am not sure, we will see! But i really want to have fun and bond with you guys!👌❤️ 

So here are the rules

▫️ the duration of this giveaway will be 7 days 

▫️ you need to follow @fidankim 
▫️ repost you favorite painting of mine and mention @fidankim in that story
▫️ like and comment my last reel

By the end of the last day ( 9th of September 9am US time) i will calculate the winner using a special app so that everything us transparent🙏🏻🤔 i will share with you in my stories the whole process!

YOUR PRESENT! I will create a fun sketch of yours and then i will turn it into digital sketch so that i can send it to you and you can afterwards use it as you wish!
For example you make it your Phone case or Tshirt and etc❤️‍🔥😍👌 

I am super excited! Good luck to all of you! Feel free to share this post with your friends 🎨🥰

Dragons was always an integral part of my art, pretty much in every painting i did i aded an element of a Dragon🐉 

It symbolizes beauty, power and wisdom to me, i love dragons,they inspire me my whole life, That being said fairly i think 2024 will be a lucky and successful year for me and for all of you!❤️ 
This New Year i wish all of you to be strong beautiful wise and healthy! This year will be kind to everyone and i feel it!🧁 

Happy New year my loyal beloved friends!🐉❤️
